description=Autonomous AI agent-as-OS for Android. Installs peko-agent + peko-llm-daemon (+ peko-blit-test, peko-drm-test for Lane A bring-up) into /system/bin with boot-time services. v0.4.0 ships display/sensors/wifi/audio/renderer HAL + DRM master + dumb buffer (Phase 1-9). Multi-provider cloud chain, full autonomy stack, optional floating overlay app. Web UI on :8080. Verified on OnePlus 6T (fajita) / arm64.
